data.description: This is a beautiful home in a very great neighborhood, and great school district. It features a split floorplan with four bedrooms and two and a half bathrooms. It has a large kitchen with a breakfast area and also a large formal dining room.  This beautiful home sits on the lake, and includes a fully fenced in back yard, and it's nicely landscaped.  Call for more information or to schedule an appointment.
